title: Dark Frontier v1.1.1 Andrioid
description:
Hire your heroes, prepare your weapons and use all your power to defeat the incoming enemies.
Defeat three waves of enemies in each of the 90 Levels.
Combat against, zombies, goblins, orcs, ogres, skeletons, spiders, and more!
Best performance on dual core devices and up.

Highlights:
3 worlds with 9 different maps
38 types of enemies, including 9 bosses
Over 30 types of heroes
Traps, walls and amazing powers
90 levels
Over 5h of gameplay
Unique musics and sounds
High quality 3d graphics
Required Android O/S : 4.0+
